- ğŸ”— **Cross-sample integration** â€“ corrects batch effects across samples and technologies  
- âš¡ **Scalable** â€“ efficient for datasets with tens of millions of spots  
- ğŸ§¬ **Biologically interpretable** â€“ links spatial domains to cell-cell interactions and tumor evolution  

